get someone real fast to go annoy him and have people standing at all the doors to keep them open (bard works well)<br>
once the guy gets rottgrime into the clear you need to do something to make him lose agro, might want to try a timed evac or something. With lucan you just zone but this guy'd rip hell out of most of the groups that fight at the zones around there.<br>
have someone non-kos ready to hail him till everyone you don't want to fight goes home.<br>
Move everyone in and kick the hell out of him.<br>
Start rezzing the bodies.<br>
<br>
I've been in zone a few times when they did him and this seemed to be about what they went with, one of my group members even took a break to be the hailer the first time I saw it done.<br>
<br>
best of luck to you <p><A HREF="mailto:Hethral@telus.net"><IMG SRC="http://the.truthbringers.com/Images/Members/Signatures/HethralBanner.jpg" HEIGHT="150" BORDER="0"></A><BR>
