<br>
Someone else (a ranger in our case), waiting a short distance from outside pulled Rottgrime from the cleric's train, after some distance between Rottgrime and the other mobs, our mage COHed the cleric while the ranger was pulling Rottgrim to us at Skyfire zone.<br>
<br>
We were 5: the mage, the cleric, the ranger and 2 wizards, we killed him easily.<br>
<br>
